统。这个光刻机制造出来的芯片主要是用于量子计算机，可以制造出高精度的固态量子器件，以及纳米器件及材料，对量子计算机来说精度非常重要。美国造出 0.7nm 芯片，EUV 光刻机做不到"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2e70f46d9461775f506f4702fa94d728_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/555883257"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0YW0/I+HiMEpEAMaCDg1ODEyMjM0IOf/yZkGMCU4kgZAE3IJNTU1ODgzMjU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1664386124.5805287", "card_id": "Q_552466607", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些狗被吹上天但是实际很难养？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b436be1827648bb2c659365bc6c19f5e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/552466607"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I0YW0/I+HiMEpEAMaCDg1MDUzNTY0ILDt5pgGMAA4HkAUcgk1NTI0NjY2MDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1664386124.5811386", "card_id": "Q_22285509", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 450}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《霸王别姬》里 PLA 在程蝶衣破音时却鼓掌这一情节？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是黑吗？是想说他们根本不懂京剧？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c0dd3bd578f70d306e1ee90addb0267e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/22285509"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I0YW0/I+HiMEpEAMaBzEwOTUxMTAgvMi3lQUwODikDEAVcggyMjI4NTUwOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1664386124.5818622", "